<!-- ══════════════ PAGE HERO ══════════════ -->
<div class="page-hero">
  <p style="font-size:0.8rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;color:var(--straw);margin-bottom:0.5rem;text-transform:uppercase;">Counseling & Talks</p>
  <h1>諮商講座</h1>
  <p>每一次對話，都是重新認識自己的機會。</p>
